title: Ten Must Have Essential Classical Albums [-emidius-]
description:
The included are considered by many to be some of the top essential Classical albums of all time. Regardless of any album rankings...these are truly MUST OWN albums for anyone interested in Classical. I hope you enjoy this collection and I will be releasing further collections in the near future.

1. Wagner's Der Ring des Nibelung



2. Beethoven's Symphonies Nos 5 & 7



3. Britten: War Requiem



4. JS Bach: Goldberg Variations



5. Puccini: Tosca



6. Elgar: Cello Concerto



7. Wagner: Tristan und Isolde



8. Tchaikovsky: Symphonies Nos 4-6



9. Gershwin: Porgy and Bess



10. JS Bach, Yo Yo Ma: Six Suites for Unaccompanied Cello
